net.sf.jclal.activelearning.multilabel.querystrategy

Class MultiLabelDensityDiversityQueryStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclal.activelearning.querystrategy.AbstractQueryStrategy
      • net.sf.jclal.activelearning.multilabel.querystrategy.AbstractMultiLabelQueryStrategy
        • net.sf.jclal.activelearning.multilabel.querystrategy.MultiLabelDensityDiversityQueryStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IConfigure, IQueryStrategy, JCLAL

    public class MultiLabelDensityDiversityQueryStrategy
extends AbstractMultiLabelQueryStrategy
    Implementation of Density Diversity query strategy for multilabel learning. The similarity values are pre-computed efficiently.
    Author:
    Oscar Gabriel Reyes Pupo, Eduardo Perez Perdomo
